comments: O'Neale (BKN) loses control of the ball as he attempts to pass, resulting in a turnover.
O'Neale (BKN) is absorbing the initial contact that occurs with Melton (PHI) and incidental contact occurs as Melton attempts to move over the pick.
Embiid (PHI) legally contests Bridges' (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) brings his off-arm toward Bridges (BKN) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away during the drive.
Tucker (PHI) steps forward and marginal foot contact occurs with Finney-Smith (BKN) as he pursues the loose ball.
Finney-Smith (BKN) initiates contact with Melton's (PHI) lower body, which affects his SQBR as he attempts to pass.
Dinwiddie (BKN) brings his hands toward Melton (PHI) and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Dinwiddie (BKN) legally contests Maxey's (PHI) jump shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Tucker (PHI) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Tucker (PHI) initiates contact with his left hand to Dinwiddie's (BKN) body during his driving shot attempt.
Dinwiddie (BKN) and Melton (PHI) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off ball.
Dinwiddie (BKN) contests Maxey's (PHI) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Maxey (PHI) moves alongside Dinwiddie's (BKN) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) cleanly blocks the shot attempt before it touches the backboard or reaches its apex.
Bridges (BKN) commits a take foul on Tucker (PHI).
O'Neale (BKN) inbounds the ball in under 5 seconds.
